{"tid":1456203,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[即討]而家係要諗點救人!","createTime":"2019-08-12T09:50:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T10:23:17.000Z","uid":105042,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"443750b1c9819690aad3eaaf16c3c14ff85704fd","tid":1456203,"uid":105042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:50:51.000Z","msg":"機場入面一定有人留,亦都會有人走,再傾去留無意思。<br />\n而家最大問題係機場如果真係封島，我地要點救人。入面已經太多狗，圍魏救趙已經唔係救人嘅辦法，搵車隊又怕有黑警混入，我地應該點做？<br />\n<br />\n除咗入去一齊面對，係機場外面應該要有人ready，唔好比佢封青馬。<br />\n班禽獸清場就一定，我地要集中救人，受過傷嘅人已經太多，唔想再見到比琴日更恐怖嘅場面。<br />\n<br />\n以下開放救人討論"},{"pid":"c04b92a5299f53982e2a88cb95b87c67cd0978d1","tid":1456203,"uid":105042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:51:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a1e502c70694854c200f06a322d6a6922dbed47","tid":1456203,"uid":105042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:52:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9b6da19d3052b091634d5b3ba23ce6b3d0efacb","tid":1456203,"uid":105042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:53:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"617ad8596d17d6569f8ed8420a51d81f06b139b0","tid":1456203,"uid":105042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:55:37.000Z","msg":"燈都熄埋"},{"pid":"217aec7d5107a6e1d2780184d2d663c6be9aa6aa","tid":1456203,"uid":113784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:55:49.000Z","msg":"1. 我哋目的係向外宣傳，冇機冇旅客，等於冇宣傳<br />\n<br />\n2. 我哋目的可能係癱瘓機場，依家所有班機都取消，已經癱瘓咗機場<br />\n<br />\n留低有咩做？？自己問下自己。<br />\n<br />\n到時機場回復運作咪再入過囉，更加唔好講夜晚收工接力的手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2af2334efdb73ef9011259a74be5f366392852f","tid":1456203,"uid":105042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci